<h4 id="toc3"><span>Other</span></h4>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[+]&nbsp;Secure&nbsp;Facility&nbsp;Dossier:&nbsp;Reliquary&nbsp;Area-27&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[–]&nbsp;Put&nbsp;Away</a></div>
